title: 16 metal+carbon patterns V3 ~ Diva of Design
description:
Here is the third set of metal and carbon pattern set. It's a premium patterns pack for Photoshop. Works only in CS2+ versions of Photoshop, and no I did not make this set myself. I purchased them from a designers website. They are high quality, and very useful. Enjoy! ~ DH
CONTENTS: .pat file to load the patterns to photoshop. Source files as JPG and PSD formats. Help file to load, define and use the patterns. This poster as PSD and JPG file, Layered PSD files ( you can change shape and color of patterns )
